parameters.name: 夜・夜中・ちょっと怪しげ【真夜中の目覚め】

parameters:
Ameria, who was crouching in Roselitte's bosom, shook her
head in response.

\n<Lyric>"Hey, Ameria. Can you make something filling for the
stomach? Portable food just isn't satisfying enough."

\n<Roselitte>"Hehe... Lyric, don't complain so much. Everyone has their
weaknesses, let's give it a rest."
\n<Ameria>"...As expected, Roselitte-san, you're kind. I like you..."
Ameria curled up even smaller and clung to Roselitte.

\n<Lyric>"I get that you're scared, but you're not a child... Well,
it's fine. It's easier if you cling to Roselitte."
Ameria clung to Lyric with a changed complexion.

\n<Lyric>"Whoa!? What is it, are you emotionally unstable or
something!?"
\n<Ameria>"--I... I need to pee! Come with me to pee!"
\n<Lyric>"Huh? Just go right there. I'm not going anywhere."

\n<Ameria>"No, I can't... I've been holding it for so long! Please,
come with me!"
\n<Roselitte>"I'll go with you. Come on, quickly."
\n<Ameria>"I can't ask Roselitte-san to do something so embarrassing!"
\n<Lyric>"What? It's okay if I do it?"
\n<Ameria>"Lyric is fine with this sort of thing, right?"

\n<Lyric>"Huh?... Ah! I'm getting heated up! I'm a pure and demure
girl, you know. I can't be involved in such unrefined
matters!"
\n<Ameria>"Then I'll just let it leak here!"

parameters.name: 迫りくる緊急自体・要脱出

parameters:
\n<Lyric>"Hey!! Stop it!! If you're going to do it, get away from
me!!"

parameters.name: 夜・夜中・ちょっと怪しげ【真夜中の目覚め】

parameters:
\n<Lyric>"Ah... I panicked. Seriously, I was more panicked than when
facing the Grim Reaper. I almost got covered in pee."

\n<Lyric>"Don't cry, we made it in time. Besides, I'm the one who
feels like crying here."

\n<Roselitte>"It can't be helped. Ameria, wait just a moment. I'll treat
you to some delicious food."

\n<Roselitte>"Yes. I'll make what we talked about before. When you're
feeling down, it's good to eat something tasty. Eat this and
cheer up."
\n<Lyric>"Oh! That sounds great. Can I get my hopes up?"
\n<Ameria>"Wow... yeah, yeah! I'm looking forward to it!"

\n<Roselitte>"Then, please wait just a little bit. I'll catch it right
away."
\n<Ameria>"Catch? Is it some kind of meat?"

\n<Roselitte>"Whether it's meat or not... Anyway, it should be easy to
find. Please wait."
\n<Lyric>"Caught it...? But that's a slime monster..."

\n<Ameria>"You don't mean... you're not going to cook that, are
you...?"

\n<Roselitte>"It's an emergency ration from Valm, used during wartime.
Normally, it's just served as is and a bit bland, but if you
do this..."

parameters.name: 包丁・包丁差しにおさめる

parameters: \n<Roselitte>"Chop it up in the right amount, grill it, and season it..."

Roselitte handed over the dishes filled with slime to the
two of them.

\n<Ameria>"Ugh... what is this... slime jelly and... huh? What's this
frothy solid thing...?"

\n<Lyric>"Roselitte... I mean no disrespect, but this is considered
food... right?"
\n<Roselitte>"How rude. It may look a bit odd, but it's a proper dish."
Saying so, Roselitte took a bite of her portion of slime.

\n<Roselitte>"--Mmm, delicious. My seasoning is popular even among my
subordinates. Now go ahead, eat it before it gets cold."

\n<Roselitte>"...Aren't you going to eat? I think it turned out quite
well..."

While Roselitte enjoyed the slime with apparent relish,
Ameria and Lyric exchanged glances--
They put the slime in their mouths.

parameters.name: 夜・夜中・ちょっと怪しげ【真夜中の目覚め】

parameters:
\n<Lyric>"Mmm... Delicious! Really, your cooking is beyond reproach,
Ameria!"
\n<Ameria>"Geez... you're so noisy when you're hungry, Lyric."

\n<Lyric>"Leave her be, leave her be. Ameria's cooking is too good
for such an uncultured palate."
